title: Chris Brown's 17-Month-Old Daughter Is a Dance Machine
text:
​First, North West was spotted going to ballet with Kim Kardashian . Then Blue Ivy was snapped on stage with her mother, Beyoncé . And let us not forget Stephen Curry's daughter, Riley, schooling us in the art of the Nae Nae . Now Chris Brown's 17-month-old daughter, Royalty, joins the celebrity-kid dance club with this adorable routine, filmed during a recent photo shoot. Dad Chris dances too, but it's really all about Royalty:
 ❤️
A video posted by @chrisbrownofficial on Oct 13, 2015 at 8:21am PDT
The cutest.
